sentences.en: Don't make a commitment to the uncommitted.
sentences.cn: 不要轻率地对未做承诺的男人做出承诺.

sentences.en: For example, can this transaction see uncommitted writes from other transactions?
sentences.cn: 例如, 这个事务能否看到其他事务未提交的写数据?

sentences.en: I was still uncommitted to the venture when we reached Kanpur.
sentences.cn: 我们到达坎普尔时，我仍未拿定主意是否去冒险。

sentences.en: I'm uncommitted tonight. Shall we go for a drink?
sentences.cn: 今晚我有空, 我们去喝一杯好 吗 ?

sentences.en: I'm uncommitted tonight. Shall we go to the movies?
sentences.cn: 今晚我有空, 我们去看电影好 吗 ?

sentences.en: It pays to stay flexible, unattached, and uncommitted.
sentences.cn: 基因宁愿为保持灵活 、 独立和自由付出些代价.

sentences.en: Our professional ethic enjoins us to stay uncommitted and report the facts.
sentences.cn: 职业道德要求我们要保持中立,报道事实真相.

sentences.en: Read uncommitted - Permits dirty reads but not lost updates.
sentences.cn: 未授权读取-许脏读取,但不允许更新丢失.

sentences.en: Read uncommitted — Permits dirty reads but not lost updates.
sentences.cn: 未授权读取-允许脏读取,但不允许更新丢失.

sentences.en: Sequential stream cannot be created for uncommitted text or image data.
sentences.cn: 无法为未提交文本或图像数据创建连续流.

sentences.en: She will join the club later, but at the moment wants to remain uncommitted.
sentences.cn: 她迟些将加入俱乐部, 但目前仍想保持自由.

sentences.en: Some workers remain uncommitted to the project.
sentences.cn: 有些工人仍未对该计画做出承诺.

sentences.en: The uncommitted op amp has its noninverting input connected to the GND pin.
sentences.cn: 闲置(我理解,看你的应用场合)的放大器反向输入端要接到地上.

sentences.en: Uncommitted output in the response buffer is automatically cleared before the forward.
sentences.cn: 响应缓存中未提交的输出在转发之前自动清空.

sentences.en: Weed out the uncommitted whiners and complainers early.
sentences.cn: 尽早剔除那些抱怨叫苦者.
